data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Felder Creek! This stunning property offers a multitude of upgrades and features that are sure to impress. Situated on a generous corner lot, this property offers ample outdoor space for gardening, play, or relaxation.Once inside, you'll notice the open-concept floor plan that effortlessly flows from the living room through the dining room and into the kitchen. Tall 9-foot smooth ceilings grace the home, providing an abundance of natural light throughout.The well-appointed kitchen features stainless steel appliances, adding a touch of modern sophistication. Prepare your meals on stunning granite countertops that not only look beautiful but are also easy to maintain.Upstairs, you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.The primary suite is a true retreat with an ensuite bathroom that features a soaking tub, a separate stand-up shower, and dual vanities, allowing you to unwind in style.  If you're in need of a dedicated workspace, you'll love the built-in office nook upstairs, perfect for those who work from home or require a quiet place for study. Additionally, storage won't be an issue with ample built-in space throughout, ensuring a neatly organized home. The garage features a built-in workbench that's sure to impress DIY pros!   This home is zoned for award-winning schools and is ideally located within 15 minutes of Historic Summerville, offering a taste of local history, and is within 7 minutes from a plethora of shops and restaurants located in the vibrant Nexton community.
